Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.70,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord2.25\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:34.84,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}The Rainy Sky - A Glass Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:46.53,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:49.32,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:13.77,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:22.61,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:26.74,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:28.43,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:32.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.04,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:40.05,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.08,0:23:40.05,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:45.88,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:45.88,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:52.26,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:58.01,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:02.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what am I doing wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:26.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:37.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:38.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And your dog tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:38.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:39.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:40.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:40.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tissues?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:41.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:42.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency rations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:45.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:46.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:47.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Handgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand grenades?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kidding, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:58.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you thought about it for a second, you would have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:04.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't funny, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:09.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have been getting along really well recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:13.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio is just like an anxious mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the list for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:24.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission is to enter town and purchase the items on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having pot-au-feu for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come straight home, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:55.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This the first time we've gone into town together, isn't it, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:04:01.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is basically my first time going to town...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:08.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:14.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was completely different during the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's a calm, quiet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:29.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:32.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing was a Nue. It's a roof ornament regional to Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to ward off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:43.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Second was a water fountain. It was modeled after the twelfth Helvetian Archduke, Akira Arcadia II.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:48.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:52.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders were to drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:57.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do know everything, Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming in or not? Would you make up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:10.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blocking the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the lady I met during the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Young{\i0} lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Coercion. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:25.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as stiff-necked as ever, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least call me Naomi, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So the next shipment is next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And does that girl know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:57.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange as ever, you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean you're soldiers-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:07.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You were obsessed with it when you first got here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:09.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but... Can I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:39.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fish, isn't it? What kind is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what was it-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:48.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dolphin. An animal more like humans than fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:51.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A type of sea mammal from when the ocean still had animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean? They lived in the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:05.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That old gaffer's good at making stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:09.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as much of a romantic as his face isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the person who made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:17.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a factory a bit from town. That's where I get all this glassware.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see them make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:22.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:23.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:35.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why. You had the factory make parts for the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:40.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We also had Naomi collect old parts for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:44.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're just amazing, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fixing that complicated machine just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:48.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:55.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a hard time just trying to remember the bugle signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:59.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really that difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:04.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because machines won't cross you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are! Your change is ¥2,750,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do we get that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Our change is ¥2.75.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:21.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharp as always, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:24.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been playing the morning bugle lately, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:32.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sorry I'm still bad at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it... I wake up completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:51.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just thinking that I need to learn so I don't cause problems for the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:05.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:09.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... Oh, sor-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! You ran into someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl at the festival!\NThat clumsy girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:46.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya, these two had nothing to do with your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:49.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the same! Soldiers disgust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:56.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of town already! Blowing that crappy bugle every single morning - you suck already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:06.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy was orphaned during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be why, but when he sees soldiers, he just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers. That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:41.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:47.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:00.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:05.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I enlisted, I took the Oath of Paradores.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I knew what it meant, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:15.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it right from the start! I can't start doubting myself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:23.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I need to put time into it and get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be chaos without bugle signals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:39.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, Noël! I've never seen a building that big before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this one's no good either?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some aberration?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:06.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The refraction should be just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:16.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kanata Sorami, a new recruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And, um, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:26.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So about what time does it throw the error?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The seek time is about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The distortion in the peripheral regions was far less,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:32.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but compared to last time the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:38.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he gets down to something about work, he just won't care about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:41.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that gaffer Carl is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:48.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of only five artisans in our nation with the title Meister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:53.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He even won a competition in the capital and presented his work to the Archduke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! If you're talking, you're not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry there, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:05.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even deserve the title, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:08.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:13.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The lens for the Takemicaduchi's optical sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To restore the Takemicaduchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:21.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I need two exactly like it. So I requested a duplicate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're this pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This lens isn't just silicon oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:33.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's infused with sodium oxide and magnesium oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This corrects chromatic and peripheral aberrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it corrects distortion in the refracted image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:42.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know the distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:48.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like a magic item from an ancient past, this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:56.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought glass was just pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's hard to make, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:04.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In Seize, there are high-quality silica deposits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:09.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,so it always had small workshops where artisans produced their goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:13.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But as the war grew more violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:19.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the need for glass for military uses increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:23.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this workshop expanded during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:37.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:40.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I like machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:41.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:45.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes machines can hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, the Takemicaduchi probably
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,killed hundreds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:57.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think machines for killing people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,really are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe what's really scary isn't the machines,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:11.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but the people who used them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look at this bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like that when I play it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:20.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but when Rio plays it, it sings beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:22.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think tanks are the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And a while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:32.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio let me hear a song from the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}It sang so beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Takemicaduchi was a good tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Let's-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:18.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably stayed up all night again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:21.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël works so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:23.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to fix the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:27.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is a real artisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:33.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If she weren't, I would never have taken this crazy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Put this on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:43.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you two went by Windmill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Miss Naomi doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:51.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She called the gaffer a wonderful romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so it sounds. Isn't that nice, master gaffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:59.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up! Hurry and get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:03.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he's mad! Back to work, back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that old technology really that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:20.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the boss always says,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:24.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"No matter how amazing it is, humans made this!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:28.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"There is no reason why we can't make it!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:45.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure is a huge difference between your bugling and Rio's trumpeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:50.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always thinking about it. What should I do to bugle like Rio does?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm practicing as hard as I possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:56.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look at my lips, they're all swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:05.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I try to play, the sound won't come out like Rio's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:08.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I just don't have talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:14.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Talent is the worst excuse for those who give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:15.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:19.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about trumpets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:25.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one mistake the young ones always make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:26.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:29.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,are you trying to force the sound out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:02.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to make it this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:03.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It wants to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Meister Carl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:50.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the sound echo the way it wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:45.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the sun came out a bit earlier for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That young lady's quite an artisan too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:21:03.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The tone glass makes changes based on the type and amount of impurities infused into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ears can't hear the difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:11.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone with perfect pitch should.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata can test each of the samples you've made
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:16.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,to find the one with the closest sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If she does, we might just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.04,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:23.26,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,listen to their voices, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.44,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:47.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël has changed quite a bit since she came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:30.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen Noël smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:14.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,405)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: A Mountain Hike - The End of the World
